messages.messageBody:
Yes, my 9 year old gets looks from older girls and they are so nice to him. Too nice in my opinion! My kids have the big blue eyes, people used to say to my husband, "that's so sick, get those colored contacts out!" and my husband would just laugh because he doesn't own colored contacts..<g> We are both Norwegian. And then through in my half of Irish, wahoo!!
Kelli
Tia Leschke <leschke@...> wrote:> In fact, the whole of Scandanavia. I spent some time back-packing
> in Norway, Sweden and Denmark and my eyes were out on stalks
> the whole time. I met a rather yummy Dane called Sven but thats a
> whole nother story....

I've got a son who is a quarter Swedish, 2 quarters German, and a quarter
English. Talk about good looking! And he's very tall for his age (15) so
he gets older girls chasing after him. Yikes! Then again, his mother
hankered after a younger man (by 7 years). In fact that's where the lad
came from. <G>
Tia
